==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dressing table
<hw>Dressing table</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a table, usually having a
vertical back piece containing a mirror, at which a person may sit while
dressing or applying makeup, and on which articles for the toilet stand.
It often has drawers for toiletries, clothing, or accessories. It is
also called a <altname>vanity</altname> or <altname>vanity
table</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dressmaker</ent>⟦br⟧
